## 📝 설계 패턴

### 패턴 1: 문자열 검색과 치환

```rust
struct TextProcessor {
    content: String,
}

impl TextProcessor {
    fn new(content: String) -> Self {
        TextProcessor { content }
    }

    // 검색: 모든 출현 위치
    fn find_all(&self, pattern: &str) -> Vec<usize> {
        self.content
            .match_indices(pattern)
            .map(|(i, _)| i)
            .collect()
    }

    // 치환
    fn replace(&mut self, from: &str, to: &str) {
        self.content = self.content.replace(from, to);
    }

    // 단어 수
    fn word_count(&self) -> usize {
        self.content.split_whitespace().count()
    }
}

// 사용
let mut doc = TextProcessor::new(
    String::from("Rust is fast. Rust is safe.")
);
println!("위치: {:?}", doc.find_all("Rust"));
doc.replace("Rust", "Cargo");
println!("단어: {}", doc.word_count());
```

### 패턴 2: 커맨드 파싱

```rust
fn parse_command(input: &str) -> (String, Vec<String>) {
    let mut parts = input.split_whitespace();
    let cmd = parts.next().unwrap_or("").to_string();
    let args: Vec<String> = parts
        .map(|s| s.to_string())
        .collect();
    (cmd, args)
}

// 사용
let (cmd, args) = parse_command("start --port 3000");
println!("명령: {}", cmd);
println!("인자: {:?}", args);
```

